---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Container from "../components/common/Container.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Why Sulav Yatra Exists"
  description="Learn the story, vision and purpose behind Sulav Yatra and our mission to become one of Nepal's most authentic and trusted travel platforms."
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <Container>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
          <h1>Why Sulav Yatra Exists</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Because some journeys are worth documenting.
          </p>
          <p class="hero-summary">
            Sulav Yatra is being built slowly and intentionally to become one of Nepal's
            most authentic, trusted and reliable travel platforms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>

    <section class="intro-section">
      <Container>
        <div class="intro-card">
          <div class="intro-copy">
            <span class="section-kicker">The purpose</span>
            <h2>Exploring Nepal should feel easier, clearer and more reliable.</h2>
            <p>
              Sulav Yatra exists to explore, document and share Nepal through practical travel guides,
              local stories and authentic experiences.
            </p>
            <p>
              What began as an ambitious travel project in 2018 has evolved into something simpler and
              more meaningful: a long-term effort to make discovering Nepal easier, more reliable and
              more enjoyable for everyone.
            </p>
            <p>
              At the same time, our vision remains clear. We aspire to become one of Nepal's most
              authentic, trusted and reliable travel platforms—connecting travelers with destinations,
              experiences, culture and practical information they can genuinely depend on.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="intro-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <img
              src="/images/branding/sulav-yatra-social-share.webp"
              alt=""
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="visual-note">
              <strong>Built for Nepal travel</strong>
              <span>Guides, stories, culture and practical information.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <Container>
        <div class="content">
          <section class="story-block decorated-block">
            <span class="section-kicker">Beyond famous routes</span>
            <h2>Every Journey Has A Story</h2>

            <p>
              Nepal is often introduced through its highest mountains, famous trekking routes and
              well-known destinations.
            </p>

            <p>
              But Nepal is much more than that.
            </p>

            <p>
              It is a country of small villages, hidden trails, local festivals, family-run businesses,
              cultural traditions and countless stories that rarely make it onto the internet.
            </p>

            <p>
              Many of these places deserve to be discovered. Many of these stories deserve to be remembered.
            </p>

            <p>
              We believe travel is not only about reaching a destination. It is also about understanding
              the people, culture and experiences that make that destination meaningful.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="story-block timeline-block">
            <span class="section-kicker">Since 2018</span>
            <h2>The Evolution Of Sulav Yatra</h2>

            <div class="timeline-list">
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <span>2018</span>
                <p>
                  Sulav Yatra began as a travel startup project with a vision of making travel in Nepal
                  more accessible and connected.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <span>Different chapters</span>
                <p>
                  Over the years, it took many forms—travel services, community building, social media storytelling,
                  content creation and video content.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <span>Lessons learned</span>
                <p>
                  Like many independent projects, the journey was not always straightforward. Some ideas worked,
                  others did not. Life changed, priorities shifted and the project evolved through different chapters.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <span>Today</span>
                <p>
                  Sulav Yatra enters a new chapter—focused on building a strong foundation of travel knowledge,
                  meaningful content and trusted information for anyone interested in exploring Nepal.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="focus-section">
            <span class="section-kicker">What we cover</span>
            <h2>What We Focus On Today</h2>

            <div class="focus-grid">
              <a class="focus-card" href="/places-to-visit-in-nepal">
                <span>01</span>
                <h3>Places To Go</h3>
                <p>Destinations, hidden gems and travel routes across Nepal.</p>
              </a>

              <a class="focus-card" href="/things-to-do-in-nepal">
                <span>02</span>
                <h3>Things To Do</h3>
                <p>Experiences, adventures, cultural activities and local recommendations.</p>
              </a>

              <a class="focus-card" href="/nepal-travel-essentials">
                <span>03</span>
                <h3>Travel Essentials</h3>
                <p>Practical information that helps travelers plan with confidence.</p>
              </a>

              <a class="focus-card" href="/articles">
                <span>04</span>
                <h3>Culture & Stories</h3>
                <p>Festivals, traditions, communities and the people that make Nepal unique.</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="principles-section">
            <span class="section-kicker">How we build trust</span>
            <h2>Our Principles</h2>

            <div class="principles-grid">
              <div>
                <h3>Accuracy Over Hype</h3>
                <p>We prioritize useful, reliable and well-researched information over trends and sensationalism.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3>Local Perspective</h3>
                <p>We believe local stories, communities and knowledge deserve a place online.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
                <p>We do not claim to know everything. Sulav Yatra grows through exploration, research and experience.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3>Respect For Nepal</h3>
                <p>Every destination, community and culture deserves to be represented thoughtfully and respectfully.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="split-section">
            <div>
              <span class="section-kicker">Slow foundation</span>
              <h2>Building Slowly, Intentionally</h2>
              <p>
                Sulav Yatra is not being built overnight.
              </p>
              <p>
                We believe meaningful projects are created one article, one destination and one story at a time.
              </p>
              <p>
                Rather than chasing rapid growth, we focus on building a strong foundation that can serve travelers for years to come.
              </p>
              <p>
                Every guide we publish, every destination we document and every story we share brings us one step closer to our vision of becoming a trusted travel resource for Nepal.
              </p>
            </div>

            <aside class="quote-card">
              <span>Our belief</span>
              <strong>The journey itself matters.</strong>
              <p>
                We are building Sulav Yatra through patience, curiosity and consistent effort.
              </p>
            </aside>
          </section>

          <section class="partners-section">
            <div class="partners-copy">
              <span class="section-kicker">For local partners</span>
              <h2>Supporting Better Travel Connections</h2>
              <p>
                As Sulav Yatra grows, we hope to work with guides, homestays, local businesses,
                creators and communities who care about responsible and meaningful travel in Nepal.
              </p>
              <p>
                The goal is not only to publish information, but to help travelers discover authentic experiences
                while giving local knowledge a stronger digital presence.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="partner-card">
              <h3>Have a local travel business, experience or story?</h3>
              <p>
                We are building the foundation now. If your work helps travelers understand Nepal better,
                we would love to hear from you.
              </p>
              <a href="/travel-partners">Become a Travel Partner →</a>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="looking-ahead">
            <span class="section-kicker">The road ahead</span>
            <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>

            <p>
              Today, Sulav Yatra is focused on documenting Nepal through travel guides, cultural stories and practical information.
            </p>

            <p>
              Tomorrow, we hope to contribute even more—helping travelers discover authentic experiences, supporting local communities and creating a platform that makes exploring Nepal easier and more connected.
            </p>

            <p>
              The destination is important. But so is the journey. And we are just getting started.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="cta-box">
            <span class="section-kicker">Join the journey</span>
            <h2>Explore Nepal. Share Stories. Keep Discovering.</h2>
            <p>
              Whether you are a traveler, local explorer, guide, photographer, writer or simply someone who loves Nepal,
              we invite you to be part of the journey.
            </p>
            <div class="cta-actions">
              <a class="primary-action" href="/contribute">Become a Contributor</a>
              <a class="secondary-action" href="/travel-partners">Become a Travel Partner</a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  main {
    background: #fffdf8;
  }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 6.5rem 0 4.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 16% 18%, rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.18), transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 84% 18%, rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.14), transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf8 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 72px 72px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, black 18%, transparent 95%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: -110px;
    width: 460px;
    height: 460px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.14);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 48px rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.04),
      0 0 0 96px rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.035);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow,
  .section-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .lead {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.42rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .hero-summary {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #334155;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .intro-section {
    padding: 4rem 0 1rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .intro-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 0.9fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: stretch;
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
    border-radius: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92));
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
  }

  .intro-copy {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .intro-copy h2,
  .content h2 {
    margin: 0.85rem 0 1.3rem;
    color: #102033;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .intro-copy p,
  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.35rem;
    color: #243041;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .intro-visual {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 420px;
    border-radius: 26px;
  }

  .intro-visual img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .intro-visual::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 15%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72));
  }

  .visual-note {
    position: absolute;
    left: 1.2rem;
    right: 1.2rem;
    bottom: 1.2rem;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.56);
    color: white;
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  }

  .visual-note strong,
  .visual-note span {
    display: block;
  }

  .visual-note span {
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    opacity: 0.82;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0 7rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 28%, rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.07), transparent 24%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 90% 74%, rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.08), transparent 28%),
      #fffdf8;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-block,
  .focus-section,
  .principles-section,
  .split-section,
  .partners-section,
  .looking-ahead {
    margin-top: 5rem;
  }

  .decorated-block {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2.4rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
    border-radius: 28px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92));
    box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
  }

  .decorated-block::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    right: 1.5rem;
    top: 1.5rem;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.16), transparent 68%);
  }

  .timeline-block {
    padding-left: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.2);
  }

  .timeline-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 150px 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
  }

  .timeline-item span {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .timeline-item p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .focus-grid,
  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .focus-card,
  .principles-grid > div {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 1.65rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .focus-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
  }

  .focus-card span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .focus-card h3,
  .principles-grid h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    color: #102033;
  }

  .focus-card p,
  .principles-grid p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .split-section,
  .partners-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 360px);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .quote-card,
  .partner-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 12%, rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.18), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), #005f9c);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.22);
  }

  .quote-card span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .quote-card strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .quote-card p,
  .partner-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
  }

  .partners-section {
    padding: 2.4rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
    border-radius: 32px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92));
    box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
  }

  .partner-card {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 12%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16), transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #f07d00, #d86600);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .partner-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .partner-card a {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .looking-ahead {
    padding: 2.4rem;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 84% 20%, rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.1), transparent 30%),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
  }

  .cta-box {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    padding: 3.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.12);
    border-radius: 32px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 16%, rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.14), transparent 32%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 22%, rgba(240, 125, 0, 0.14), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f8fafc);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }

  .primary-action,
  .secondary-action {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 0.95rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .primary-action {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  .secondary-action {
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 113, 186, 0.22);
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .intro-card,
    .split-section,
    .partners-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .intro-visual {
      min-height: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .focus-grid,
    .principles-grid,
    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .intro-copy,
    .decorated-block,
    .partners-section,
    .looking-ahead,
    .cta-box {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>